al.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c1633%2c20220526%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,111,聲,1633,20220526,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"1633","JDATE":"20220526","JTITLE":"聲請定其應執行刑"}